Never run or compile as root.

=[ Introduction

Inspired by libraries as LibSecRm and THC-SecureDelete and scrub, Polly The
Wiper aims to be a mix of them and bring them to a higher level of
awesomeness!!11

File wiper.
Swap and memory wiper, also in realtime.
Obfuscating library calls.

More to come soon.

